99
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:18,040
No, but you've confirmed her drawings
will do too.

100
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,000
She drew well.

101
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,920
You wanted her in the first place.

102
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,360
Jiang Junnan,

103
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:23,240
