104
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:25,000
You were defeated over a dozen times.

105
00:04:25,430 --> 00:04:26,870
Don't change the topic.

106
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:31,680
Still, the way Yue Qianling blew up

107
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,560
